{"tid":487250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港之光) 惠英紅榮登亞洲視后","createTime":"2017-12-02T15:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T05:09:13.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"353ec1b0ba4b71003ba72a7d88a373fe876cdadc","tid":487250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"《人間有情之苦瓜的味道》是香港電台的劇集<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171202/bkn-20171202214804203-1202_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171202%2Fbkn-20171202214804203-1202_00862_001.html&d=Qp05Lx6YjSJ46TstKj3jbW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f8d86215\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171202/bkn-20171202214804203-1202_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再下一城！惠英紅新加坡初奪視后寶座<br />\n12月02日(六) 21:48<br />\n<br />\n藝人惠英紅今年十一月憑電影《血觀音》首次奪得台灣金馬影影后殊榮，估唔到惠英紅拎獎繼續拎唔停，尋日憑電台劇集《人間有情之苦瓜的味道》勇奪「第二十二屆亞洲電視大獎2017」的「最佳女主角」，初嘗視后寶座！<br />\n<br />\n頒獎典禮尋日於新加坡舉行，雖然惠英紅面對六位強勁對手，如：日劇天后篠原涼子、台灣視后柯桂嬿以及新加坡視后鄭惠玉等，但仍勇奪視后寶座！但出爐視后惠英紅因為工作關係，未能親身領獎，她接受東網訪問時說：「喺香港拍緊戲，所以冇時間去現場，呢套劇其實自己好鍾意，覺得自己真係做得好好，呢部係一部勵志、正面嘅劇集，所以自己好開心。（心情如何？）無時間興奮，因為其實開緊工，拍緊感情戲，所以知道嗰陣咪『哦』咁樣囉！」而視帝則由台灣男星蔡振南憑劇集《媽媽不見了》而奪得。"},{"pid":"0a814a9ab2563b4e360a6aa008890b3966aeb52e","tid":487250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de94fa10802e1ba6a8a997a137c1aa0700ec583","tid":487250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f715a99ce71d12e5f362ad89183cace8a274403","tid":487250,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3b18c25a38b93ab20ee2e10ecd03b552dbcb198","tid":487250,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全力支持小紅姐"},{"pid":"2bf86e4988b4cb1a988083e328df3e62432a2b86","tid":487250,"uid":56459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"套野好好睇<br />\n香港上大家記住支持"},{"pid":"b43b780b35f3309c925f171d49d0a0b63221cb89","tid":487250,"uid":14816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:51:22.000Z","msg":"小紅姐命中率到底有幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩年真係入圍=中獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f52376d2629c8f7292d28f1411adf01bcd44f2","tid":487250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902dd705700a69c6fd5dd1282f89d2a3505364ba","tid":487250,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"個獎都幾威喎<br />\n幾乎拎親都係大中華區既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6530ddcc3190c9a6ff281ffea9bec578066af597","tid":487250,"uid":146720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"bobby都拎到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bad6a0e10ef8d81f631aefb0ade2fb5ace6c247","tid":487250,"uid":50984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim